NOTE ON docs/ CONTENT

The Chinese-language D&D rule text under `docs/` is NOT covered by the MIT
license above. Those files originate from the community translation project
"DND 五版不全书" (DnD 5e Bu-Quan-Shu).

- Original rules: copyright Wizards of the Coast.
- Translation: copyright the 不全书 translation team and contributors.
- This repository merely references that material as a data source for the
  Claude Code skill. We make no claim to either copyright and charge no fee.
- If a rights holder wishes the material removed, please file an issue at
  https://github.com/ZGP0072600/dnd5r-skill/issues and the relevant content
  will be taken down.

Please support official WotC publications and the 不全书 translation team
where you can.
